INSTRUCTIONS FOR BUILDING LEVELDB ON WINDOWS / MSVC++
[Tested with Microsoft Visual C++ 2010 Express](http://www.microsoft.com/visualstudio/en-us/products/2010-editions/visual-cpp-express)

1. Open a Visual Studio Command Prompt :
   Start Menu -> "Microsoft Visual Studio 2010 Express" > "Visual Studio Command Prompt"

2. Change the directory to the leveldb project

2. To build a static lib, run: `msbuild /p:Configuration=Release`

